ore":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"咩都唔做最好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"個人認為都要篤嘅，最起碼都要俾其他人知道呢仆街個樣同身份<br />\n但建議齋圍，唔好用索帶？<br />\n<br />\n真心討論"},{"pid":"040d3ea6ae6d065bdb1902e34e045daee105aade","tid":1467111,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14fe23948d807228df1ad204d142e831c0f9e0de","tid":1467111,"uid":234588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48c1f40dab9a2cc8ed5d055f84e800ecba1d8116","tid":1467111,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"咩都唔做最好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"個人認為都要篤嘅，最起碼都要俾其他人知道呢仆街個樣同身份<br />\n但建議齋圍，唔好用索帶？<br />\n<br />\n真心討論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:54.000Z","msg":"咁咪又係會起衝突"}]}